@aBuiltIn(lispClass="integer",
          doc="t_integer")
public class cINTEGER
extends cRATIONAL
implements tINTEGER

cINTEGER Implements all integers, so difference between bignums and fixnums will be programmaticaly set (class, tests, etc)

Author:
Ivan Pierre {ivan@kilroysoft.ch}, George Kilroy {george@kilroysoft.ch}
